 * tests/persist/gpu/GpuStorageNodeUTest.cxxtest
 *
 * Basic store/fetch round-trip tests for GpuStorageNode.
 * Modeled after atomspace-rocks BasicSaveUTest.cxxtest.
 *
 * Tests Phase 1: atoms and values survive a round-trip
 * through GPU SoA pools.
